eu.stratosphere.nephele.template

Interface InputSplitProvider


  • public interface InputSplitProvider
    An input split provider can be successively queried to provide a series of InputSplit objects an AbstractInputTask is supposed to consume in the course of its execution.
    Author:
    warneke

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      InputSplit getNextInputSplit()
      Requests the next input split to be consumed by the calling AbstractInputTask.

    • Method Detail

      • getNextInputSplit

        InputSplit getNextInputSplit()
        Requests the next input split to be consumed by the calling AbstractInputTask.
        Returns:
        the next input split to be consumed by the calling AbstractInputTask or null if the AbstractInputTask shall not consume any further input splits.
